||0||0||0||0||1||0\n|-\n|[[Walsall F.C.|Walsall]]\n|[[1992\u201393 in English football|1992\u201393]]\n|Third Division\n|39||21||1||0||4||1||4||2||48||24\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[Shrewsbury Town F.C.|Shrewsbury Town]]\n|[[1993\u201394 in English football|1993\u201394]]\n|Third Division\n|28||11||2||0||3||0||1||0||34||11\n|-\n|[[1994\u201395 in English football|1994\u201395]]\n|Third Division\n|31||11||0||0||2||1||1||0||34||12\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!59!!22!!2!!0!!5!!1!!2!!0!!68!!23\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Career Total\n!444!!141!!30!!1!!32!!10!!14!!6!!520!!158\n|}\n\n{{refbegin}}\n:A.&nbsp;{{note|Other}} The \"Other\" column constitutes appearances and goals in the [[FA Charity Shield]], [[Football League Trophy]], [[Football League play-offs]], [[Full Members Cup]] and [[UEFA Cup]].\n{{refend}}\n\n==Honours==\n*with '''Wolverhampton Wanderers'''\n**[[Football League Second Division|Second Division]] promotion [[1982\u201383 in English football|1983]]\n*with '''Birmingham City'''\n**[[Football League Second Division|Second Division]] promotion [[1984\u201385 in English football|1985]]\n**Club's leading scorer [[1984\u201385 in English football|1984\u201385]], [[1986\u201387 in English football|1986\u201387]]\n*with '''Everton'''\n**[[Football League First Division|First Division]] champions [[1986\u201387 in English football|1986\u201387]]\n**[[FA Community Shield|FA Charity Shield]] winners [[1987 FA Charity Shield|1987]]\n*with '''Shrewsbury Town'''\n**[[Football League Third Division|Division Three]] (level 4) champions [[1993\u201394 in English football|1993\u201394]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Soccerbase}}\n* {{NeilBrownPlayers|player/wayneclarke}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Clarke, Wayne}}\n[[Category:English footballers]]\n[[Category:English football managers]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:Wolverhampton Wanderers F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Birmingham City F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Everton F.C. players]]\n[[Ca