013]])</small>\n* George Pascua <small>([[2014 PSL season|2014]]\u2013[[2016 PSL All-Filipino Conference|2016]])</small>\n* Cesael delos Santos <small>([[2016 PSL Grand Prix Conference|2016]]\u2013[[2019 PSL season|2019]])</small>\n* Emil Lontoc <small>([[2020 PSL Grand Prix Conference|2020]]-present)</small>\n\n==Transactions==\n{{collapse top|2019 Season|bg=navy|fc=white}}\n{{col-beg}}\n{{col-3}}\n\n===Grand Prix===\n====Addition====\n* [[Denden Lazaro|Dennise Michelle Lazaro]] <small>([[Cocolife Asset Managers]])</small><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.foxsports.ph/volleyball/superliga/963590/denden-lazaro-joins-petron-in-pursuit-of-first-psl-title/|title=Denden Lazaro joins Petron in pursuit of first PSL title|date=2019-01-08|website=FOX Sports Philippines|language=en-US|access-date=2019-01-17}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://volleyverse.com/phi/psl-grand-prix-w/denden-lazaro-joins-petron-blaze-spikers/|title=Denden Lazaro joins Petron Blaze Spikers {{!}} PSL Grand Prix|date=2019-01-08|website=Volleyverse|language=en-US|access-date=2019-01-17}}</ref>\n* [[Stephanie Niemer]] (''Import'') <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.foxsports.ph/volleyball/superliga/939818/psl-stephanie-niemer-announces-return-for-grand-prix-2019/|title=PSL: Stephanie Niemer announces return for Grand Prix 2019|date=2018-11-13|website=FOX Sports Philippines|language=en-US|access-date=2019-01-17}}</ref>\n* [[Katherine Bell (volleyball)|Katherine Bell]] (''Import'') <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.philstar.com/sports/2018/11/16/1869127/katherine-bell-confirms-return-petron-psl|title=Katherine Bell confirms return to Petron in PSL|website=philstar.com|access-date=2019-01-17}}</ref>\n\n====Subtraction====\n* [[Ria Duremdes]] <small>([[FEU Lady Tamaraws]])</small>\n* [[Cherry Ann Rondina]] <small>([[UST Growling Tigers#The UST Golden Tigresses Volleyball Team Pool|UST Golden Tigresses]])</small>\n{{col-3}}\n\n===Invitational===\n====Addition====\n*\n\n====Subtraction====\n* \n{{col-3}}\n\n===All-F