67290.jpg|80px]]{{refn|group=n|name=tri|Triangular}}\n|-\n|St Georges||SE8||Yes||{{refn|group=n|Bounded by the Thames, a boat repair marina and the roads named Deptford Wharf and Plough Way, St George\u2019s Square in SE8 has no homes or businesses.}}\n|-\n|[[Trinity Church Square|Trinity Church]]||SE1||Yes||[[File:Trinity Church Square - north side - geograph.org.uk - 847609.jpg|80px]]{{refn|group=n|Half of Trinity Church Sqaure is Henry Wood Hall, an Arts Organisation which replaced the church.}}\n|-\n|Montague||SE15||Yes||\n|-\n|Peabody||SE1||Yes||[[File:Peabody Square Model Dwellings, Blackfriars Road.jpg|80px]]\n|-\n|Sutherland||SE17||Yes||[[File:Sutherland Square, SE17 (geograph 2668688).jpg|80px]]\n|-\n|Peckham||SE15||Yes||[[File:Peckham Square - geograph.org.uk - 1741872.jpg|80px]]\n|-\n|Granville||SE15||Yes||\n|-\n|Yarnfield||SE15||Yes||\n|-\n|Choumert||SE15||Yes||\n|-\n|Vivian||SE15||Yes||\n|-\n|[[Pygmalion and Galatea (play)|Galatea]]||SE15||Yes||\n|-\n|Huguenot||SE15||||\n|-\n|Shard's||SE15||No||{{refn|group=n|A narrow asphalted accessway}}\n|-\n|Dickens||SE1||Yes||\n|-\n|Hamilton ||SE1||Yes||\n|-\n|Fountain Green||SE16||Yes||[[File:Fountain Green Square (geograph 2127509).jpg|80px]]\n|-\n|[[Bonnington Square|Bonnington]]||SW8||Yes||[[File:Bonnington Square Garden - geograph.org.uk - 1397632.jpg|80px]]\n|-\n|[[Addington Square|Addington]]||SE5||Yes||[[File:Addington Square SE5 - geograph.org.uk - 165917.jpg|80px]]\n|-\n|Rust||SE5||Yes||\n|-\n|Foxley||SW9||Yes||\n|-\n|Nightingale||SW12||Yes||[[File:Nightingale Square, Balham (geograph 3262823).jpg|80px]]\n|-\n|[[Lorrimore Square|Lorrimore]]||SE17||Yes||[[File:St Paul, Lorrimore Square, London SE17 - geograph.org.uk - 1750513.jpg|80px]]\n|-\n|[[Flat Iron Square|Flat Iron]]||SE1||No||<ref>[http://maps.google.co.uk/maps?q=flat+iron+square|,+london&hl=en&ll=51.503938,-0.094795&spn=0.002551,0.004823&sll=52.8382,-2.327815&sspn=10.149213,19.753418&t=h&hq=flat+iron+square|,&hnear=London,+United+Kingdom&z=18 Flat 